ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectPort Hope and District Chamber of Commerce - Ontario ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the PORT HOPE AND DISTRICT CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in Ontario, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the Town of Port Hope to the Municipality of Port Hope, from Hamilton Road to the West until East Townline Road; from Lake Ontario to the North until Rice lake/Eagleson 1st Line.
